rows.name:
Please bring Bidibi
some Linka Honey.

rows.label: qst002902_msg0002
rows.name:
Do not need anything else.
Bidibi give to Dibidi.

rows.label: qst002902_msg0004
rows.name:
This enough Linka Honey for
Bidibi to bathe in!

rows.label: qst002902_msg0005
rows.name:
Even though Bidibi was
tricky-fooled into coming to
such a place, it worth it in end.
